title: Saints Defeated in Straight Sets by Eagles
text:
Saints Defeated in Straight Sets by Eagles 
By Norman Seawright III October 24, 2015 Updated Oct 24, 2015 at 8:06 PM CDT 
Duluth, MN (NNCNOW.com) -- The St. Scholastica (CSS) volleyball team fell to Upper Midwest Athletic Conference (UMAC) rival Northwestern for the tenth straight time. 
Although Kortney Morrin led the team with digs (14) and kills (10), the Eagles swept the Saints (0-3).
